'''''I Told You So''''' ni firime yo muri Gana yo mu 1970<ref>https://tugamedia.com/i-told-you-so-first-ever-ghanaian-movie-lady-in-80s/</ref>. Filime yerekana abanya [[Gana]] nuburyo bwabo bwo kubaho muburyo bwo gusebanya<ref>https://www.ghanafilmindustry.com/i-told-you-so-ghanaian-film-noir/</ref> <ref>https://mubi.com/fr/films/i-told-you-so</ref>. Iratanga kandi ubushishozi mubuzima bw'umukobwa ukiri muto utakiriye inama za se mugihe agiye kurongora umugabo<ref>https://www.graphic.com.gh/entertainment/showbiz-news/i-told-you-so-to-play-at-conference-centre.html</ref>, ntacyo yari azi kumugabo agiye kurongora, ahubwo yakiriye inama za nyina na nyirarume kuko agendera k'ubutunzi n'imbaraga umugabo afite<ref>https://hyperleap.com/topic/I_Told_You_So_(film)</ref>.

Uyu mukobwa ukiri muto yaje kumenya ko umugabo agomba kurongora yari igisambo cyitwaje imbunda<ref>https://www.newday.com/film/i-told-you-so</ref> . Ntiyishimiye ibyabaye byose. Papa abajije uko byagenze, asubiza ko umugabo yagombaga kurongora ari umujura witwaje imbunda; ise yarangije avuga ati "Nakubwiye gutya"<ref>http://ghanarising.blogspot.com/2013/06/classic-ghanaian-film-i-told-you-so.html</ref>.   

